9128bfe7629c2902c6c3aa9","url_token":"a-fang-suo-38","name":"阿方索","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/6642cd5749128bfe7629c2902c6c3aa9","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563510140","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1ef1cbedb5e862c9b6f3c176acdeac43_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546244963,"updated_time":1546244963,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这条评论点赞和评论较多发出来看一下\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e记得六年级想过一个关于无限循环小数的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e10/3＝3.3循环，左端乘以10,右端乘以10；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后第二个式子减去第一个，，这样他俩好像不相等……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-708f03da2e5cb66a507dc61d8818b78c_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2248\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9ff2fc701eb3589c646b886b816775eb_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-708f03da2e5cb66a507dc61d8818b78c_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='2248'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2248\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9ff2fc701eb3589c646b886b816775eb_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-708f03da2e5cb66a507dc61d8818b78c_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-708f03da2e5cb66a507dc61d8818b78c_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e额，然后有很多人不理解我解释一下\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就是说，第二个式子乘以10之后它会比第一个少了一个3所以感觉无限循环小数的理论是有错误的\